snippet: Goalie Roberto Luongo, who lost his job to Cory Schneider during the playoffs, is practicing with the Canucks while the team tries to find a trading partner.
abstract: Vancouver Canucks goaltender Roberto Luongo, replaced by teammate Cory Schneider during 2012 playoffs, arrives in Vancouver for practice while team tries to find a trading partner.
lead_paragraph: Goalie Roberto Luongo, who lost his job to Cory Schneider during the playoffs, is practicing with the Canucks while the team tries to find a trading partner.

headline.seo: Luongo Arrives in Vancouver but May Not Stay Long
headline.main: Goalie Arrives in Vancouver but May Not Stay Long
